name: NTRMAN Style Lora
description:
NTRMAN Style Lora. This is a request from my lora request form. I recommend using Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix and at 0.75 - 0.45 Strength. Faces are a little messy, to fix use Hires. fix.

Trigger word: ntrman

Loras used in order:
Palutena Kid Icarus Lora
Jill Valentine RE5 Lora
Tracer (Overwatch) LORA
Mercy (Overwatch) LORA
Ann Possible from Kim Possible Lora
Courtney Total Drama Island Lora

I created a Lora request form. Please do not submit anything that breaks the tos. Thx!
